 Freshly blended fruit smoothies of various colors and tastes in glass jars in rustic wooden tray. Yellow, red, green. Top view, selective focus It is advised to eat fruits or drink smoothies as consuming fruits has many advantages: detoxifies the body, replenishes energy, aids in digestion and weight loss, and prevents dehydration, and skincare, amongst others. Smoothies can be consumed in the morning or at night, before bed. INGREDIENTS METHOD